OL,5, Royal Mail workers will stage two      
OL,6, 48-hour strikes around Black Friday and
OL,7, Cyber Monday in a row over pay, jobs   
OL,8, and conditions.                        
OL,10,FThe Communication Workers' Union (CWU) 
OL,11,Fwill recommend around 115,000 of its   
OL,12,Fmembers reject a pay offer of around 9%
OL,13,Fspread over two years.                 
OL,15,FBut the union cancelled two strikes on 
OL,16,F12 and 14 November, saying it wants to 
OL,17,Ftake more "proportionate" action.      
OL,19,FRoyal Mail urged workers not to strike 
OL,20,Fat the "busiest time of the year".     
